# 7. 願うことは

Kohane: (Here should be okay, right?)
Kohane: (Normally, I'd practice somewhere closer to the station since there's usually more people...)
Kohane: (No, don't rush yourself... All you've been doing is singing by yourself in your room...)
Kohane: (I have to start by getting used to singing in public.)
Kohane: Let's see... I can play my music through my phone's speakers...
Kohane: Okay.
Kohane: ♪————!
Kohane: ♪——! ——! ——!
Kohane: (After that event, An sent me a lot of messages.)
Kohane: (But...)
Kohane: ♪ ————...
Kohane: (If I can't sing on stage, then surpassing a legendary event...)
Kohane: (Making An's dream come true... I can't do any of that.)
Kohane: (So...)
Kohane: (I have to overcome this...!)
Kohane: ♪——————————!
Kohane: Huff... Huff... Huff...
Kohane: I'm still nowhere near her level.
Kohane: (An made my heart race every time I heard her sing...)
Kohane: (I had so much fun whenever we sang together. I thought anything was possible for us...)
Kohane: (And I was so happy when she started calling me her partner.)
Kohane: (I know it's probably too late now.)
Kohane: (But for now...)
Kohane: I have to keep trying.
Kohane: ♪————~~!
Kohane: (I thought I'd be able to come here early today since we didn't have classes...)
Kohane: (But my committee duties ended up taking longer than expected.)
Kohane: It's been so long since I last came here.
Kohane: (Even if it's from afar, I have a feeling that hearing An's voice will help motivate me more.)
Kohane: (But...)
Young People: Hahaha. You're kidding, right?!
Kohane: ...!
Kohane: (This place... I'm still a little scared of it...)
Kohane: (I never felt afraid whenever I was with An, but...)
Kohane: (I'll be fine... As long as I walk off towards the side, no one should notice me...)
???: Huh? Hey, aren't you that girl who was always singing with An?
Kohane: Eep!
Kohane: Uhh, I...
Live House Staff A: Hey, don't scare her like that. Sorry, we didn't mean to startle you.
Live House Staff B: I-I'm really sorry...! I sort of couldn't help it after I realized that you were An's partner...
Kohane: Oh...
Live House Staff A: You two were such a great duo. Despite having starkly different personalities, you were able to draw the best out of each other.
Live House Staff B: Yeah, and An's been singing all by herself recently. It'd be great to see you to sing together again.
Kohane: (They remember when we were still Vivids...)
Kohane: (But...)
Kohane: U-Umm... Th-The thing is...
Kohane: Right now, I... I can't sing...
Kohane: But I want to be able to again... Someday...
Live House Staff B: Oh...
Live House Staff A: Is it a touchy subject?
Kohane: I'm sorry.
Live House Staff A: No, you don't need to apologize.
Live House Staff A: That being said... It is unfortunate.
Live House Staff A: I mean, you were An's first partner.
Kohane: ...
Live House Staff B: Sorry for keeping you. Don't stay out too late, okay?
Kohane: O-Okay...! Thank you...
Kohane: (I was her first partner...)
Kohane: (Is it okay for me to tell her?)
Kohane: (That I want to get a lot better...)
Kohane: (That I want us to sing together again someday.)
???: ♪——! ♪——————~~~~!!
